                        <p>Folios 81v sqq.: seliḥot le-lel Tsom ha-Kipur. Folios 98v sqq.: seliḥot le-shaḥarit Tsom ha-Kipur. Folios 113r sqq.: tefilat musaf. Folios 126r sqq.: tefilat ha-minḥah. Folios 132v sqq.: seliḥot le-minḥat Tsom ha-Kipur. Foilos 136v sqq.: tefilat ne῾ilah. Folios 141r sqq. : seliḥot li-ne῾ilah le-rabi Binyamin. Folios 142v sqq.: seliḥot le-aḳedah.  </p>
                     
                     
                     
